parameters: I'm fine, but we don't have that much time.
This is a once in a lifetime opportunity.
Did you forget, already. I've only been
reminding you everyday since before we even
knew each other existed. There's no way!
Don't you want me to like get you some high
level artifact that nobody's ever heard of?
If im the one who just remembered it...
All woman must have some sorta thing
for knocking me upside my damn head.
That's supposed to mean what exactly?
While I was running here, some rogue lady
tripped me and got me for a 100 beans.
I know when you're lying to me.
To be honest, I left my quest book at your spot.
So when I got there Key handed it over.
She broke up with you but, oddly, is holding your keys.
Don't worry about her; she's a womanizer.
Turns out a lot of men are like that too.
